{"url": "https://people.com/style/caroline-wozniacki-engaged-to-david-lee-see-the-ring/", "text": "Michael Bezjian/Getty; Inset: Caroline Wozniacki/Twitter\n\nCaroline Wozniacki has found love \u2014 and it\u2019s far from the kind you see on the tennis court.\n\nThe 27-year-old Danish tennis champion just announced her engagement to her fianc\u00e9, NBA player David Leeof the San Antonio Spurs. Lee popped the question while the two were on vacation in Bora Bora \u2014 and it wasn\u2019t long before Wozniacki showed off the sparkler on Instagram, revealing a very large oval diamond, which takes up the majority of her first knuckle, and is flanked with by a channel-set diamond band.\n\nRELATED PHOTOS: The Best Celebrity Engagement Rings\n\nWozniacki captioned the announcement, \u201cHappiest day of my life yesterday saying yes to my soulmate @Dlee042\u201c\n\nLee soon followed Wozniacki\u2019s post with a photo of the couple, writing, \u201cShe said YES! So thrilled to be engaged to my soulmate! \u2764\ufe0f\ud83d\udc8d\u201d\n\nThe two had sparked relationship rumors earlier this year, and finally made their relationship public this past summer.\n\nBefore Lee, Wozniacki was previously engaged to golf star Rory McIlroy. The former couple ended their engagement soon after announcing the news in early 2014.\n\nWhat do you think of Wozniacki\u2019s ring? Sound off in the comments section, below.\n\nSaveSave\n\nSaveSave", "images": ["https://people.com/thmb/ja0pSLSYP7kOFX6bCDtmc0fnxFo=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():focal(959x509:961x511)/nia-long-ime-udoka-6e09def0f1194abaad5b685d94f658ce.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/fJbH7Lkxti_FXTqyc-oVKKZovzA=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():focal(749x19:751x21)/olivia-culpo-fiance-41323-5-fa1ac7cf957743da9ca3c9620f80cf3c.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/TiWDadk0TxY8Z3dKWjLUrXOUxQc=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():focal(919x494:921x496)/sofia-richie-elli